  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  symptomatic and ambulatory patients

          -  suffering from knee osteoarthritis (ACR criteria)

          -  25&lt;BMI&lt;35

          -  signed informed consent

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  need to surgery within 6 next months

          -  co-morbidity
